          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1642010773127-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1642010773127-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1642010773127-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add 80ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[120ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[160ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> to a bowl with<strong> half </strong>your<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>marinade</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>diced chicken thigh</strong> to the <strong>marinade</strong> and give everything a good mix up then set aside until later</p><p>Tip: This will help to tenderise your chicken!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1642010785732-x200.jpg",
