      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong> to a separate bowl with your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>grated garlic</strong>, the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> </strong>1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> ranch-style dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
