        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>chicken</strong> from the marinade, discard the marinade</p><p>Add your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>ground turmeric </strong>to the bowl and mix it all up</p><p>Add your <strong>cornflour </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix until the chicken is fully coated</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
