            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once the pan is very hot, add the <strong>coated chicken </strong>and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden, crispy and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>popcorn chicken</strong></p><p>Once crispy, transfer to kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
