    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, layer the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>sliced cucumber </strong>and<strong> drained sweetcorn </strong>in rows</p><p>Top with the<strong> egg quarters </strong>and<strong> popcorn chicken </strong>– this is your<strong> popcorn chicken cobb salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> ranch-style dressing </strong>over everything</p><p>Let everyone dig in!</p>",
